title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Searching for solutions to lifes big questions might lead you to unconventional approaches now. You possess a burning need to learn more about yourself and the world around you, especially your origins and deep aspects of your psyche. You possibly even sense that youre close to finding the answers, too. Perhaps its the tenacity of the Taurus Moons beaming trine with probing Pluto that resembles your own resolve to look wherever you can for clues, whether it's past-life regression, Eastern philosophy, neuroscience, or your therapists couch. Enjoy the tough and satisfying work of cultivating self-awareness. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
